commit.message: Allow whitespaces in C format strings.
Docstring in c module for callable signatures.
Fix segfault giving dict names as non-list.
Fields of zero bits are not allowed.
Removed performance tests since they are slow.
Replace INT_MAX with 0x7fffffff for windows to hopefully work. Not perfect...
byteswap() in C for 1, 2, 4 and 8 bytes.
Offset range check and slightly faster padding packing.
